<p>In December 2025, our Clearwater team came together to support Toys for Tots during the holiday season. They donated toys and volunteered their time to help bring a little extra joy to children and families at Christmas.</p>

<h2>Making the season brighter</h2>
<p>Giving back is something that means a lot to our team, and this effort was all about making the holidays brighter for kids who deserve to feel the excitement and magic of the season. Every donation and every hour volunteered helped make that possible.</p>
<p>We are proud of the Clearwater team for stepping up, supporting their community, and helping spread some well-deserved holiday cheer.</p>
